    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>If you can already see the SQL being printed, that means you have the code below in your hibernate.cfg.xml:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;property name=\"show_sql\"&gt;true&lt;/property&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>To print the bind parameters as well, add the following to your log4j.properties file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>log4j.logger.net.sf.hibernate.type=debug\n</code></pre>\n"
