    "question_id" : 2536829,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Worth noting that the code you see is sent to the database as is, the queries are sent separately to prevent SQL injection. AFAIK The ? marks are placeholders that are replaced by the number params by the database, not by hibernate.</p>\n"
